title: Living Artist Of Today -  Contemporary Art Vol1.pdf
description:
Living Artist Of Today: International Contemporary Art Vol.1
Art & Beyond Studio | 2012 | ISBN 18887954274 | English | 90 pages | PDF | 12.3 MB

International Contemporary Artists is a collection of modern art, a source for artists, galleries, museums, art collectors who seek for the new trends in the world of art. International Contemporary Artists art book includes distinguished samples of the featured artists' work and information about them, each one representing different trends of art. The book has been created by Eve Lemonidou and Olga Antoniadou, publishers and curators
